Charlie Creed-Miles https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Charlie_Creed-Miles 0 Charlie Creed-Miles (born 24 March 1972) is an English actor and musician.Creed-Miles was born in Nottingham, and had his first starring screen role, aged 19, in The Punk (1993). His relationship with actress Samantha Morton (with whom he co-starred in The Last Yellow) produced a daughter, born in 2000.
